window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Imagine \"Back to the Future\" fused with the chaos of an alien invasion, told with the narrative brilliance of John Scalzi or Octavia Butler.</p> <p>Time is not just a dimension, but a playground of fate and destiny. Faer Michelson is a man blessed and cursed with vivid and inescapable memories. From a childhood accident that opened a door to another realm, to mysterious encounters with a woman whose hair holds the colors of the rainbow, Faer's life has been anything but ordinary.</p> <p>When a photograph surfaces showing a teenage Faer in a time and place he has no memory of, he is thrust into an interdimensional quest that challenges his understanding of reality. When Faer has a premonition of his own death he has to navigate a complex web of galactic politics, lizard aliens, telekinetic powers, and a best friend whose turned into a ghost.</p> <p>Faer must piece together the fragments of his past to save his future. His journey is an exploration of family memories, the pain of lost loves, and the hope of redemption. Each revelation brings him closer to understanding his true purpose and the interconnectedness of all life.</p> <p>Miranda Levi's \"A Tear in Time\" is a riveting tale that blends the excitement of time travel with the emotional depth of a family saga. With its rich character development and intricate plot twists, this novel will keep you enthralled until the final tick. Perfect for fans of time-bending adventures and heartfelt storytelling, \"A Tear in Time\" is a must-listen that explores the timeless question of how our choices shape our destiny.</p> <p>Dive into a narrative where every second counts, and the past, present, and future are more intertwined than ever imagined. Experience the thrill the complexity of love and the unyielding bond of family in a story that transcends time itself.</p>"; 
